content: Another claim is "After April 11 , 2020 , there was a fatality rate of over 1.61 % in Malaysia during the coronavirus pandemic ." And the evidences are ["Accelerated testing reveals a comparatively low case fatality rate ( 1.61 % as of 11 April 2020 ) than in the Philippines and Indonesia , but remains moderately more severe than in Thailand , Singapore and Brunei."]
